commandFlags.name: Command name
commandFlags.permissions: Array for necessary permissions or style, probably don't use with roleOnly
commandFlags.roleOnly: Array for necessary role ids or style, probably don't use with permissions
commandFlags.roleEnglish: Array for necessary roles for command description
commandFlags.args: Flag for if the command needs arguments
commandFlags.usage: Arguments for the usage for command description
commandFlags.cooldown: Command cooldown in seconds, default stored in defaultCooldownTime
